review_text: I am not satisfied with the  quality of material used  in JAC X-200. There are daily issues in quality of material, Its headlights switch has been out of order only after 1 year.  The main part of rear excel which  moves the vehicle was also out of order due to which I have to change it and mechanic was telling that this is the main issue in all JAC vehicles.
